v2.0.1
Updated for CK3 1.18.4 compatibility (bumped through 1.18.2, 1.18.3).
No conflicts with mod files. All 33 tradition references, 5 ethos references
preserved in base game.

v2.0
Updated for CK3 1.18.* compatibility.
Bundled legacy track artwork from "More Legacies Art +" (https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2977838440).
All 10 legacy tracks now include custom icons and illustrations.
Fixed typo: "Prolofic Flirt" → "Prolific Flirt" in English, French, and Russian localizations.
Fixed incorrect modifier keys in German, Spanish, Korean, and Chinese localizations.
Added Japanese and Polish localization support (complete translations).
All 9 supported game languages now have complete, proper translations.
Removed deprecated commented code (~300 lines of House Traditions remnants from v1.2-v1.4).
Code cleanup and optimization.
Note: For scrollable legacy display GUI, use the companion mod "Scrollable Legacies".

v1.10
Updated scheme modifiers for the scheme rework.

v1.9
Added Chinese localization thanks to Marcus.

v1.8
Added Korean localization thanks to WKML.

v1.7
Added English localization placeholders for other languages: French, Korean, Russian, and Chinese.

v1.6
Added German localization thanks to positief161.

v1.5
Added the bld (bravelildragon) prefix to all legacies for compatibility purposes.

v1.4
Removed the ability for House Traditions to determine legacy availability to make it a separate patch and clean up the error logs for people not using House Traditions.
Fixed the designation of the following traditions to make legacies available as intended: Performative Honour, Family Business, Expert Artisans, Dexterous Fishermen, Seafarers, Linguists, Recognition of Talent.

v1.3
Added Spanish localization thanks to Kordi. Updated for v1.7.1.

v1.2
Removed the AI choosing legacies based on their House Traditions. Hopefully this improves stability.

v1.1
Added localization for the Temptation - Sweet Corruption and Witchcraft - Initiation perks